# TODO

## Description

The goal of this app is to build a dual facette application, with:
    - A view only mode for all the people that may be interested by the world build by the author(s). It should be very beautiful, very fast (no loading screens, images loading instantly, no freezes, ...), responsive (the app working well on computer, phones, tablets, but maybe also on other TVs like a smart TV or other devices).
    - An editor mode for the wiki creators so they can very easily add more content or edit existing content. The editor mode will be hidden for the view only users. The editor mode will be automatically detected based on if the user is running the python editor server locally on his computer.

So currently, the app is divided on 5 pages with each some subpages:

- The main menu page where the user lands when opening the wiki
- A document & story page where the user can manage all each elements (JSON files), but also a document section where the user can write stories, TODOLIST, prepare all its lore, etc.
- A character page where the user can manage character sheets.
- A world & map page where the user can manage places.
- A timeline & events page where the user can manage timeline and events.

